爱莎贝儿-148CM-L 粉肤 RAD045 望月利世Mochizuki Rize-紫色花园那貌美的妻子
她剪枝时哼着走调的歌，晨光追着花洒头一跳一跳。
风卷起睡袍带子缠上花骨朵，她俯身去解，颈后碎发间露出一小片被吻过的淡红。
你指尖残留的香氛气息混在一起，分不清是花香在染她，还是她在浸透整座花园。
胸型：148CM-L 粉肤

Elsa Babe-148CM-L Pink RAD045 Mochizuki Rize-The Beautiful Wife in the Purple Garden
She hummed an off-key song as she pruned the trees, the morning light dancing on the showerhead.
The wind whipped up the sleeves of her robe, tangling them around the buds. She bent down to untangle them, revealing a small patch of kissed pale red between the strands of her broken hair at the back of her neck.
The lingering fragrance of your fingertips mingled with the scent, indistinguishable whether it was the floral aroma influencing her, or her own fragrance permeating the entire garden.
Body type: 148CM-L with Pink skin tone.
